{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369640/extras/GIF_Sizeok.gif?t=1737747368\" /><br><br>Halfway between a board game and a video game, Vanova's Stories is an investigative adventure for 2 to 4 players. Do you like wacky, colorful worlds, cooperating with your friends, and narrative point-and-clicks? Then this game is for you!<br><br><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369640/extras/EN_Angel.png?t=1737747368\" /><br>Discover a hand-drawn world and explore the city of Vanova to find clues about the committed crimes. Whether in 2D or 3D, your observational skills will be your greatest assets!<br><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369640/extras/EN_Denis.png?t=1737747368\" /><br>Each location you investigate includes a number of unusual and eccentric characters. Some may refuse to talk to you... Perhaps your teammates will have better luck?<br><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369640/extras/EN_Marc.png?t=1737747368\" /><br>Agility, intimidation, strength, charm\u2014everyone has their own unique ability that will lead them to clues only they can uncover. Your adventure and dialogue options will vary depending on your detective, so choose wisely! <br><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369640/extras/EN_Stephanie.png?t=1737747368\" /><br>A suspect is refusing to talk to you, and you want to show him evidence to get him to confess? Swap clues with a teammate and get them to do it for you!<br><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369640/extras/EN_Bulles.png?t=1737747368\" /><br>Different investigations require different approaches. Each one will feature a new mechanic, forcing you to rethink the way you investigate.<br><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369640/extras/EN_Claire.png?t=1737747368\" /><br>Think you've discovered the truth? Get together with your friends and tell your boss what you've found, linking all the pieces together. Make sure everyone agrees, as a wrong hypothesis could cost you dearly.<br><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369640/extras/EN_End.png?t=1737747368\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369640/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737747368","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369640/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1737747368","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369640/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737747368","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369640/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1737747368","categories":[{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Online Co-op","id":38},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[5],"notes":"Cartoon violence"},"demos":[{"appid":3444730,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369640/extras/GIF_Sizeok.gif?t=1737747368\" /><br><br>Halfway between a board game and a video game, Vanova's Stories is an investigative adventure for 2 to 4 players. Do you like wacky, colorful worlds, cooperating with your friends, and narrative point-and-clicks? Then this game is for you!<br><br><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369640/extras/EN_Angel.png?t=1737747368\" /><br>Discover a hand-drawn world and explor